{
  "id": "RAW_d28f2131",
  "title": "GLM-5.1 高速版：400 tokens/s，顶尖模型跑出最快速度",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzI3NzQ0Mg==&mid=2247493927&idx=1&sn=3a85cdfcaa82cbd9cafc02d6d8af713e",
  "date": "2026-05-22 01:41:00",
  "author": "智谱",
  "siteName": "智谱",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260522223852_f6f57bd.jpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>Coding时代，速度是爽点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>今天，我们面向部分企业客户提供</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">GLM-5.1高速版API“GLM-5.1-highspeed”</span></span></span><span><span>。模型输出速度达到</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">400 tokens/s</span></span></span><span><span>，刷新当前全球大模型厂商API的速度上限。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>这一速度意味着，一位写作者连续伏案数天才能写完的文字量，它在1分钟内便交付完毕；一名工程师埋头敲键盘3天才能完成的开发任务，它能在喝一杯咖啡的时间里完成。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260522223852_99dbc8c.gif\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>更重要的是，在过去，“快”往往意味着“小”，高速模型几乎总是轻量级模型。GLM-5.1高速版打破了这一行业惯例，首次在国产大模型中，</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">将旗舰级能力与极致低延迟同时带入生产环境</span></span></span><span><span>，无需再为响应速度牺牲模型质量。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>我们对比了GLM-5.1高速版与GLM-5.1普通版的速度与效果，如下：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">在长程任务中，GLM-5.1高速版在30秒内完成复杂网页</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">在Agent Swarm中，GLM-5.1高速版瞬间调度50个不同人格来并行回答</span></span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;font-size: 22px;padding-bottom: 12px;\"><span><span>不是快的模型，而是快的旗舰模型</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>过去一年，国内大模型的Coding能力快速提升，而Coding恰恰是AI应用中对速度较为敏感的场景之一。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>一个Coding Agent任务往往需要经历数十轮模型调用，单轮响应只要慢上几秒，整体耗时就可能拉长十几分钟；面对长程任务的大型重构项目，每一步响应慢1秒，逐步累加又是几分钟的空等。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>GLM-5.1高速版在完整保留GLM-5.1能力的基础上，第一次拥有“即问即答”的响应速度，</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">带来的体感完全不同，模型开始真正成为一个可以实时协作的伙伴</span><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">，</span></span></span><span><span>和你坐在一起盯着画布调参。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">实测1</span></span></span><span><span>：写代码像开启了10倍速，模型能够一边理解工程上下文，一边持续生成代码与修改方案，你刚输入需求，函数、接口与调用链已经同步展开。</span></span></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">实测2</span></span></span><span><span>：玩家控制一个角色在3D地图里移动，输入文字，模型会根据输入的文字瞬时建模，场景实时改变。此前因延迟而无法实现的全新产品形态，开始真正具备落地可能。</span></span></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">实测3</span></span></span><span><span>：用户提出需求的那一刻，模型可以即时生成出恰好匹配这个需求的工具与交互，甚至可以意图判断，这正是一种新型操作系统的雏形。</span></span></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;font-size: 22px;padding-bottom: 12px;\"><span><span>速度背后：TileRT高性能推理引擎</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>GLM-5.1高速版API“GLM-5.1-highspeed”由</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">智谱GLM团队</span></span></span><span><span>与</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">TileRT团队</span></span></span><span><span>联合打造，在推理引擎、调度系统与底层基础设施三个层面进行了系统级优化：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:20px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:34px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">推理引擎层</span></span></span><span><span>：针对GLM-5.1的架构特点，重写了核心推理路径，有效提升了单卡吞吐能力；</span></span></li>\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">调度系统层</span></span></span><span><span>：通过动态批处理、请求合并和KV缓存调度优化，显著降低高并发场景下的尾延迟；</span></span></li>\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">基础设施层</span></span></span><span><span>：围绕推理集群部署、网络链路、负载均衡进行协同优化，确保400 TPS不是一个“峰值”数字，而是稳定可用的生产级能力。</span></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>模型推理速度的理论上限由硬件决定，但真实系统通常距离物理极限仍存在巨大差距。</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">核心问题在于推理框架的调度方式</span></span></span><span><span>。当前主流框架仍以operator/kernel作为基本调度单元，每个算子都要经历“host启动→读权重→计算→写回→同步”的严格完整链路。当推理进入单token、小batch、多卡TP的场景后，算子被切到微秒级，原本可忽略的调度、访存与同步开销会被迅速放大。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>TileRT的设计思路，是</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">彻底抛弃Runtime层的动态调度</span></span></span><span><span>，在编译期（AOT）将整个计算图静态编排为一个常驻GPU的persistent Engine Kernel。在单卡之内，计算、异步IO与通信被全部拆解为Tile级微任务，整个推理过程只Launch一次Engine Kernel，算子间的中间结果不再写回Global Memory，而是经由Register、Shared Memory与L2 Cache直传，host调度与跨算子同步被悉数压进同一个常驻kernel。在多卡尺度上，TileRT进一步将SM内部的Warp Specialization思路外推到整张8卡NVL拓扑。不同GPU rank不再执行同构逻辑，而是按计算密度与数据依赖被特化为不同worker。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">完整技术blog链接</span></span></span><span><span>：</span></span><span><span><a href=\"https://www.tilert.ai/blog/speed-as-the-next-scaling-law-zh.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.tilert.ai/blog/speed-as-the-next-scaling-law-zh.html</a></span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;font-size: 22px;padding-bottom: 12px;\"><span><span>面向速度敏感场景开放</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>GLM-5.1高速版适用于AI编程、实时交互、商业决策、实时语音等对响应延迟要求极高的场景，</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">现已面向智谱MaaS平台部分企业客户开放服务</span></span></span><span><span>。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>我们将持续推进推理引擎的工程优化，进一步扩大高速模型的服务能力，让更多企业与开发者与能够获得低延迟、高智能的生产级AI能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">开放平台模型页面</span>：</span></span><span><span><a href=\"https://docs.bigmodel.cn/cn/guide/models/text/glm-5.1-highspeed\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.bigmodel.cn/cn/guide/models/text/glm-5.1-highspeed</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "智谱发布 GLM-5.1 高速版 API，输出速度达 400 tokens/s，在保留旗舰模型能力的同时实现极致低延迟，并介绍了背后的 TileRT 高性能推理引擎技术。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "智谱发布 GLM-5.1 高速版 API，输出速度达 400 tokens/s，在保留旗舰模型能力的同时实现极致低延迟，并介绍了背后的 TileRT 高性能推理引擎技术。",
  "summary": "智谱于 2026 年 5 月 22 日面向部分企业客户发布 GLM-5.1 高速版 API「GLM-5.1-highspeed」，模型输出速度达到 400 tokens/s，刷新当前全球大模型厂商 API 的速度上限。该版本首次在国产大模型中将旗舰级能力与极致低延迟同时带入生产环境，打破了「快即小」的行业惯例。文章详细阐述了速度在 Coding 场景中的关键价值，并介绍了背后的 TileRT 高性能推理引擎，其在推理引擎层、调度系统层与基础设施层进行了系统级优化。TileRT 的核心设计思路是抛弃 Runtime 层的动态调度，在编译期将整个计算图静态编排为一个常驻 GPU 的 persistent Engine Kernel，从而大幅降低调度、访存与同步开销。该版本适用于 AI 编程、实时交互、商业决策、实时语音等对响应延迟要求极高的场景，已面向智谱 MaaS 平台部分企业客户开放服务。",
